<li id=default_li>To view different resources go to the two timelines in the second page or go to the information page on the last page.</li>
<li id=default_li>The first timeline on the second page is about life forms & environments, please view it if you want a better understanding of our Earth’s beginning and why we are here.</li>
<li id=default_li>The second timeline on the second page is about important historical figures, please view it if you want a better understanding of the great historical figures which brought us to the advancements that we have today. </li>
